<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <%- include('../../partials/head.ejs') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('../../partials/nav.ejs') %> <%-
    include('../../partials/topNav.ejs') %>

    <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:ml-64">
      <div class="md:py-8 mx-5 sm:mx-8 lg:mx-14 xl:mx-20">
        <div class="py-6 lg:py-10 bg-white lg:border">
          <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6">
            <div>
              <img
                class="w-32"
                src="/assets/images/CSR-A_Logo-RGB.jpg"
                alt="logo"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 text-[#00A19A] font-bold">
              <h1 class="pb-2 sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
                SHORT ACCREDITATION APPLICATION FORM
              </h1>
              <hr class="lg:border border-black" />
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 text-[#00A19A] font-bold">
              <h5 class="pb-2 sm:text-2xl">
                For applicants registered as Sole Traders and Micro businesses (1-3 people) and small charities
              </h5>
            </div>

            <div class="text-justify pt-8 lg:text-lg">
              <p>
                THIS APPLICATION FORM IS PROVIDED FOR YOU TO COMPOSE YOUR APPLICATION OFF-LINE. ONCE YOU ARE READY TO SUBMIT, GO TO THE
                ONLINE APPLICATION ON OUR WEBSITE AND ENTER YOUR ORGANISATION’S DETAILS. YOU SHOULD THEN UPLOAD THIS APPLICATION FORM
                WHERE REQUESTED. YOU SHOULD ALSO UPLOAD YOUR COLLATED, EVIDENCED DOCUMENTATION WHERE INDICATED.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 font-bold text-red-600">
              <p>
                IMPORTANT - PLEASE SAVE THIS PDF WITH THE NAME OF YOUR ORGANISATION REPLACING THE WORDS ‘YOUR ORGANISATION NAME’ IN
                THE
                FILE NAME AS SHOWN HERE:
                <br />
                CSR_A-SHORT APPLICATION FORM-(YOUR ORGANISATION NAME).pdf
                <br />
                IT IS VITAL THAT YOUR APPLICATION FORM IS TAGGED WITH YOUR NAME BEFORE SUBMITTING.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <form>
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="lg:col-span-1 lg:px-6">
                <div class="mx-5 mt-4">
                  <label class="text-sm">Contact Person</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="contact_person"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Type your name"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid text.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Organisation Name</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="organisation_name"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Type your organisation's name"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid text.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Organisation Address</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="organisation_address"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Type your organisation's address"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid address.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3 lg:mt-4 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Postal Code</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="postal_code"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Type your postal code"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid text.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="lg:col-span-1 lg:px-6">
                <div class="my-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Telephone Number</label>
                  <br />
                  <input id="telephone_number"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="tel" placeholder="Type your contact number" />
                  <p class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm">
                    Please provide your contact
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Email Address</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    disabled
                    id="email_address"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="email"
                    placeholder="Type your email"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid email address.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="my-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Mobile Number</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="mobile_number"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="tel"
                    placeholder="Type your contact number"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide your contact
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 mx-5">
                  <label class="text-sm">Nationality of Organisation</label>
                  <br />
                  <input
                    id="organisation_nationality"
                    class="peer border invalid:border-2 invalid:border-[#ff0000] invalid:outline-[#ff0000] h-11 w-full lg:h-10 border-[#00A19A] rounded-md py-1 px-3 placeholder:text-xs"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Type your organisation's nationality"
                  />
                  <p
                    class="mt-2 invisible peer-invalid:visible text-[#ff0000] text-sm"
                  >
                    Please provide a valid text.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6 pt-1 text-justify text-base">

              <div class="text-base text-[#464343] py-5">
                <div class="flex space-x-3">
                  <h1>Are You a Sole Trader/Micro (1 – 3 employees):</h1>
                  <select id="soleTraderMicro" class="border-2 px-2 rounded-lg border-[#464343]">
                    <option value="YES">YES</option>
                    <option value="NO">NO</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-base text-[#464343] py-5">
                <div class="flex space-x-3">
                  <h1>Or a Small Charity (up to £500,000 turnover):</h1>

                  <select
                    id="charity"
                    class="border-2 px-2 rounded-lg border-[#464343]"
                  >
                    <option value="YES">YES</option>
                    <option value="NO">NO</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right text-sm mt-3 text-white pr-5 lg:pr-10">
              <button
                id="submit_btn"
                onclick="updateCompanyDetails()"
                class="py-2 px-3 hover:bg-[#03857e] w-32 rounded-md shadow-lg bg-[#00A19A] transition ease-in-out delay-150 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 hover:animate-none animate-bounce duration-300"
              >
                Save
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
          <p class="mt-5 font-bold pl-5 text-red-700">
          PLEASE NOTE THAT YOUR ORGANISATION NAME SHOULD BE ENTERED IN EXACTLY THE FORMAT THAT YOU WANT IT DISPLAYED ON YOUR
          ACCREDITATION MARK AND CERTIFICATE.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- jsPDF library -->
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"
      integrity="sha512-qZvrmS2ekKPF2mSznTQsxqPgnpkI4DNTlrdUmTzrDgektczlKNRRhy5X5AAOnx5S09ydFYWWNSfcEqDTTHgtNA=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"
      integrity="sha512-BNaRQnYJYiPSqHHDb58B0yaPfCu+Wgds8Gp/gU33kqBtgNS4tSPHuGibyoeqMV/TJlSKda6FXzoEyYGjTe+vXA=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    ></script>
    <script
      defer
      src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.10.2/dist/cdn.min.js"
    ></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/others/company_details.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
